<p><a href= "https://www.georgetowncupcake.com">Georgetown Cupcakes:</a> Creativly-decorated cupcake shop. $$</p>
  <p>Eventhough Georgetown Cupcakes is not Boston based, the bakery is one of the most famous bakeries in D.C and they actually had a show called Georgetown Cupcakes! Georgetown Cupcakes is quite sweet but if you have a sweet tooth we are sure you will love Georgetown Cupcakes! If you look at the picture you will notice that Georgetown Cupcakes has a signature look that is extremly simplistic and cute! Georgetown Cupcakes is a very well known bakery and we recommend everybody trying it once!</p>
